    License: Apache License 2.0
    Used for: OCR of scorebug / clock text

  - opencv-python (optional)
    License: Apache License 2.0 / BSD
    Used for: auto scorebug region detection

  - Tesseract OCR (optional, system binary)
    License: Apache License 2.0
    Used for: text recognition when pytesseract is used

  - FFmpeg / ffprobe (external binaries, not bundled)
    License: LGPL / GPL
    Used for: video/audio decoding and encoding (invoked as separate process)

